## Common Mistakes to Avoid

### ❌ Wrong: Using localhost inside Docker
```yaml
# WRONG
DATABASE_URL: postgresql+asyncpg://coop:pass@localhost:5432/coop
# RIGHT
DATABASE_URL: postgresql+asyncpg://coop:pass@postgres:5432/coop
```

### ❌ Wrong: Using Celery in Stages 1-3
```python
# WRONG (Stage 1-3)
from celery import Celery
app = Celery('tasks', broker='redis://redis:6379')

# RIGHT (Stage 1-3)
import arq
class WorkerSettings:
    functions = [my_task]
    redis_settings = arq.connections.RedisSettings()
```

### ❌ Wrong: Blocking I/O in async functions
```python
# WRONG
async def embed(text: str):
    return model.encode(text)  # blocks event loop
# RIGHT
async def embed(text: str):
    return await asyncio.get_event_loop().run_in_executor(None, model.encode, text)
```

### ❌ Wrong: Adding enterprise services too early
```yaml
# WRONG in Stage 1-3
services:
  temporal: ...    # Stage 4 only
  neo4j: ...       # Stage 4 only
  opa: ...         # Stage 4 only
  keycloak: ...    # Stage 4 only
```

